{
  "stem": "10768.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And even though they gave him the first aid, and they-- he was very lucky because he was injured in the spine, but luckily, his spinal cord was not touched.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was injured below the spinal cord, in what is called coccyx, the, the anatomical name.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So he had a bone injury-- muscular and bone injury, but no-- no-- he was left-- he wasn't left paralyzed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "When, when I found out where my brother is, I wrote to him, and I asked him to come to the, to my hospital.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "At the same time, in Rokitnica already, somehow, either because of a general depression of what I went through, or because I had absolutely no interest to go out on the street to buy clothes, my main aim was to be in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And this, I devoted my entire time in my life to helping the injured and the people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there, somehow the gratitude from the, from the soldiers-- some came and wanted to give me gold bracelet with a ring that they maybe took somewhere from a German.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I had absolutely no sense of value.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I didn't-- it didn't interest me, gold or jewelry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "A dress from one, I said, if you can bring me a dress, because I'm sick and tired of wearing that uniform.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the white uniforms are the military.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So anyhow, this is how I was in the army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Until-- my brother came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Somehow he came, he also took a furlough for two weeks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And he came first to my hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So I was asking all the doctors at my hospital they should examine him.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
